text: Manfred Dubski (born 19 September 1954) is a retired German footballer. He made 190 appearances in the Bundesliga for Schalke 04 and MSV Duisburg as well as 210 matches in the 2. Bundesliga for Duisburg, Rot-Weiß Oberhausen and Union Solingen. == References == == External links == * Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:German footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Bundesliga players Category:2.
